strings: <voice_0x01000DE2><se_def>Legal!: The moon shoulder grants a wish once in a lifetime.
<voice_0x01000DE3><se_def>Legal!: It's so strange to see each other again.
<voice_0x01000DE4><se_def>Legal!: tell me what brings you tonight
<voice_0x01000DE5><se_def>Legal!: I know what ship you're on. I well remember when the moonlight took me to the other side of the ocean.
<voice_0x01000DE6><se_def>Legal!: Now you must send the ship back to the sea. Where are you from? the stock market
<voice_0x01000DE7><se_def>Legal!: I just remember the good times. If there is an ocean, it is the earth.
<voice_0x01000DE8><se_def>Legal!: I've seen it in Escada too...I want to remember it now. memories of the sea that sleeps on land
<voice_0x01000DE9><se_def>Legal!: Yes, yes, music can bring back memories...
<voice_0x01000DEA><se_def>Legal!: How frightened I was. Cavakin's doses are insufficient for this.
<voice_0x01000DEB><se_def>Legal!: For this you will need a larger tool.
<voice_0x01000DED><se_def>Legal!: yes i have the answer... there is atmosphere...
<voice_0x01000DEE><se_def>Legal!: I can see it! A new moon in your solar sector means you have no control over anything.
<voice_0x01000DEF><se_def>Legal!: There are better tools somewhere in the world.
<voice_0x01000DF0><se_def>Legal!: Your friends will always be there for you.
<voice_0x01000DF1><se_def>Legal!: Brave children, if you want to awaken the ancient ship, you must first find Yuek.
<voice_0x01000DF2><se_def>Legal!: Give it to me and I will remember the old sea and the ship will go back to sea.
